            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"日本政府譴責外國影響力行動 此前OpenAI披露一宗網絡輿論施壓企圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v8o9Fyoy_9BW32PNJ6LZSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/d9c946f0-13d3-11f1-9def-e907fb067639\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日本政府譴責外國影響力行動 此前OpenAI披露一宗網絡輿論施壓企圖</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
