        {
            "title": "巴基斯坦稱與阿富汗已處於「公開戰爭」狀態 中國呼籲雙方對話",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"巴基斯坦稱與阿富汗已處於「公開戰爭」狀態 中國呼籲雙方對話\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uQTY09CnmOhiuaJlhui4Tw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/bf8aa370-13d2-11f1-abe5-63e9e1534d4f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">巴基斯坦稱與阿富汗已處於「公開戰爭」狀態 中國呼籲雙方對話</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%B7%B2%E8%99%95%E6%96%BC-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD-%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B-062549139.html",
