        {
            "title": "巴郡阿貝爾談「後巴菲特時代」布局 首封股東信備受矚目",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"巴郡阿貝爾談「後巴菲特時代」布局 首封股東信備受矚目\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WOL6bwTpxRAg0wDIkuRc6w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/03da8740-283b-11f0-a7fe-7e2de3c6429e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">巴郡阿貝爾談「後巴菲特時代」布局 首封股東信備受矚目</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
